<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Gotam Ladwani — Intermediate Student | Aspiring IBA Karachi</title>
<meta name="description" content="Gotam Ladwani, Intermediate (Pre-Medical/Pre-Engineering) student, son of Deepchand Suthar. Passionate about Mathematics and Physics, aiming for IBA Karachi.">
<style>
  :root{
    --board: #1e2b26;
    --board-dark: #16201c;
    --chalk: #f3f1e7;
    --chalk-dim: #cfd0c6;
    --gold: #d3a13a;
    --blue: #7fa3ad;
    --rule: rgba(243,241,231,0.14);
  }

  *{ margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

  body{
    background: var(--board);
    color: var(--chalk);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  @font-face{
    font-family: 'FrauncesFallback';
    src: local('Georgia');
  }

  /* subtle chalkboard grain */
  body::before{
    content:"";
    position: fixed; inset:0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(255,255,255,0.025), transparent 45%);
    pointer-events:none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .formula-layer{
    position: fixed;
    inset:0;
    z-index:0;
    overflow:hidden;
    pointer-events:none;
  }
  .formula-layer span{
    position:absolute;
    color: var(--chalk-dim);
    opacity: 0.08;
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    white-space: nowrap;
    animation: drift 45s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes drift{
    from{ transform: translateY(0); }
    to{ transform: translateY(-120px); }
  }

  header, main, footer{ position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  header{
    min-height: 92vh;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:flex-start;
    padding: 8vh 8vw;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--rule);
  }

  .eyebrow{
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }

  h1{
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 7vw, 5.4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.05;
    max-width: 16ch;
    position: relative;
  }

  h1 .underline{
    position:relative;
    display:inline-block;
  }
  h1 .underline::after{
    content:"";
    position:absolute;
    left:0; right:0; bottom:-6px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--gold);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    animation: chalkline 1.4s ease-out 0.6s forwards;
  }
  @keyframes chalkline{ to{ transform: scaleX(1); } }

  .tagline{
    margin-top: 1.8rem;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.6vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--chalk-dim);
    max-width: 46ch;
  }

  .meta-row{
    margin-top: 3rem;
    display:flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2.4rem;
  }
  .meta-item{
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  .meta-item .label{
    display:block;
    color: var(--blue);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  section{
    padding: 8vh 8vw;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--rule);
  }

  .section-label{
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
  }

  .section-title{
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3.4vw, 2.6rem);
    max-width: 20ch;
    margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .subjects{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.6rem;
  }

  .card{
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .card:hover{
    border-color: var(--gold);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }
  .card .glyph{
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display:block;
  }
  .card h3{
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .card p{
    color: var(--chalk-dim);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .goal-block{
    display:flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .goal-text{ flex: 1 1 340px; }
  .goal-text p{ color: var(--chalk-dim); max-width: 52ch; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .goal-figure{
    flex: 1 1 260px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
    padding-left: 1.6rem;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }
  .goal-figure .big{
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height:1;
  }
  .goal-figure .small{
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--chalk-dim);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .family-line{
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--chalk-dim);
    line-height: 2;
  }
  .family-line strong{ color: var(--chalk); font-weight: 500; }

  footer{
    padding: 5vh 8vw;
    display:flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--chalk-dim);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    * { animation: none !important; transition: none !important; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px){
    header, section, footer{ padding-left: 6vw; padding-right: 6vw; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="formula-layer" id="formulaLayer" aria-hidden="true"></div>

<header>
  <div class="eyebrow">Student Profile</div>
  <h1><span class="underline">Gotam Ladwani</span></h1>
  <p class="tagline">Intermediate student building a foundation in Mathematics and Physics, working toward admission at IBA Karachi.</p>

  <div class="meta-row">
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="label">Class</span>Intermediate</div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="label">Goal</span>IBA Karachi</div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="label">Focus</span>Maths &amp; Physics</div>
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <section id="about">
    <div class="section-label">01 — About</div>
    <div class="section-title">Family &amp; background</div>
    <p class="family-line">
      Full name: <strong>Gotam Ladwani</strong><br>
      Father's name: <strong>Deepchand</strong><br>
      Surname: <strong>Suthar</strong><br>
      Currently enrolled in: <strong>Intermediate (Class XI–XII)</strong>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="interests">
    <div class="section-label">02 — Interests</div>
    <div class="section-title">Where the curiosity goes</div>
    <div class="subjects">
      <div class="card">
        <span class="glyph">∑</span>
        <h3>Mathematics</h3>
        <p>Drawn to problem-solving, algebra, and the logical structure behind every equation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="glyph">Δ</span>
        <h3>Physics</h3>
        <p>Fascinated by how the physical world follows precise, discoverable laws — from motion to energy.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="goal">
    <div class="section-label">03 — Goal</div>
    <div class="section-title">Aiming for IBA Karachi</div>
    <div class="goal-block">
      <div class="goal-text">
        <p>The Institute of Business Administration (IBA) Karachi is the target destination after Intermediate — a step toward a strong, analytical career built on the same discipline found in maths and physics.</p>
        <p>Steady, focused preparation now is the groundwork for that goal.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="goal-figure">
        <div class="big">IBA</div>
        <div class="small">KARACHI — TARGET INSTITUTION</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <span>Gotam Ladwani · S/O Deepchand · Suthar</span>
  <span>Built with HTML, CSS &amp; JavaScript</span>
</footer>

<script>
  // Scatter a few faint formula fragments in the background for atmosphere
  const formulas = ["E = mc²", "F = ma", "a² + b² = c²", "v = u + at", "∫f(x)dx", "PV = nRT", "x = -b ± √(b²-4ac) / 2a"];
  const layer = document.getElementById('formulaLayer');
  formulas.forEach((f, i) => {
    const el = document.createElement('span');
    el.textContent = f;
    el.style.left = (Math.random() * 90) + "%";
    el.style.top = (110 + Math.random() * 20) + "%";
    el.style.fontSize = (1.2 + Math.random() * 1.6) + "rem";
    el.style.animationDuration = (30 + Math.random() * 30) + "s";
    el.style.animationDelay = (i * 3) + "s";
    layer.appendChild(el);
  });
</script>

</body>
</html>
